<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>数字签名 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D/</link><description>数字签名 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>常见算法与场景</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BD%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%82/%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BD%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%82/%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="常见算法与场景">常见算法与场景</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：不同密码学算法有各自的适用场景和权衡点，选型时需综合考虑安全性、性能、合规性和生态系统成熟度。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="密码学算法选型需匹配场景的安全需求和性能约束避免过度设计或不足">密码学算法选型需匹配场景的安全需求和性能约束，避免过度设计或不足</h2>
<h3 id="对称加密算法选型">对称加密算法选型</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>场景</th>
          <th>推荐算法</th>
          <th>原因</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>通用数据加密</td>
          <td>AES-256-GCM</td>
          <td>安全、支持认证加密、硬件加速</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>国内合规系统</td>
          <td>SM4</td>
          <td>国密要求</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>低功耗IoT设备</td>
          <td>AES-128</td>
          <td>计算量小，安全性足够</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>文件系统加密</td>
          <td>AES-XTS</td>
          <td>针对块设备优化</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// AES-GCM 加密示例</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">Cipher</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">cipher</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Cipher</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">getInstance</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;AES/GCM/NoPadding&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">SecretKeySpec</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">keySpec</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">SecretKeySpec</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">key</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s">&#34;AES&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cipher</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">init</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Cipher</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">ENCRYPT_MODE</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">keySpec</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">GCMParameterSpec</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">128</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">iv</span><span class="p">));</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kt">byte</span><span class="o">[]</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">encrypted</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">cipher</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">doFinal</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">plainText</span><span class="p">);</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="非对称加密算法选型">非对称加密算法选型</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>场景</th>
          <th>推荐算法</th>
          <th>原因</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>HTTPS/TLS证书</td>
          <td>RSA-2048 / ECDSA P-256</td>
          <td>广泛兼容</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>移动端API签名</td>
          <td>ECDSA</td>
          <td>签名短、验证快</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>国内金融系统</td>
          <td>SM2</td>
          <td>国密合规</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>区块链/数字货币</td>
          <td>ECDSA / Ed25519</td>
          <td>签名短小高效</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="哈希算法选型">哈希算法选型</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>场景</th>
          <th>推荐算法</th>
          <th>原因</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>密码存储</td>
          <td>bcrypt / scrypt / Argon2</td>
          <td>计算慢可防暴力破解</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>数据完整性校验</td>
          <td>SHA-256</td>
          <td>快速且安全</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>数字签名</td>
          <td>SHA-256 + RSA/ECDSA</td>
          <td>标准组合</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>国内合规</td>
          <td>SM3</td>
          <td>国密要求</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="典型组合场景">典型组合场景</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>场景</th>
          <th>组合方式</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>HTTPS通信</td>
          <td>RSA/ECDHE + AES-GCM + SHA-256</td>
          <td>密钥交换 + 对称加密 + 完整性校验</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>JWT签名</td>
          <td>HS256(RSA) / ES256(ECDSA)</td>
          <td>Header.Payload 用私钥签名</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>文件加密</td>
          <td>AES-256 + RSA</td>
          <td>随机AES密钥加密文件，RSA加密AES密钥</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>数字证书</td>
          <td>私钥签名 + 公钥验签 + 证书链</td>
          <td>CA用私钥签发，浏览器用CA公钥验证</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="国密算法体系">国密算法体系</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>算法</th>
          <th>类型</th>
          <th>用途</th>
          <th>替代的国际算法</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>SM2</td>
          <td>非对称加密</td>
          <td>加密、签名、密钥交换</td>
          <td>RSA、ECDSA</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SM3</td>
          <td>哈希</td>
          <td>数据摘要、签名</td>
          <td>SHA-256</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SM4</td>
          <td>对称加密</td>
          <td>数据加密</td>
          <td>AES</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SM9</td>
          <td>标识密码</td>
          <td>基于标识的加密和签名</td>
          <td>IBE方案</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1密钥长度过短">问题1：密钥长度过短</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：使用1024位RSA或128位以下AES以追求性能
<strong>解决</strong>：RSA至少2048位，AES至少128位，密码学安全不能妥协</p>]]></description></item><item><title>密码学基础</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BD%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%82/%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%E5%AD%A6%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BD%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%82/%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%E5%AD%A6%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="密码学基础">密码学基础</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：密码学的三大基础工具是对称加密（快、共享密钥）、非对称加密（慢、公私钥分离）和哈希（不可逆、防篡改），实际系统中通常组合使用以兼顾安全与效率。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="密码学通过数学难题保障信息的机密性完整性和不可抵赖性">密码学通过数学难题保障信息的机密性、完整性和不可抵赖性</h2>
<h3 id="三大基础工具对比">三大基础工具对比</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>类型</th>
          <th>特点</th>
          <th>密钥</th>
          <th>用途</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>对称加密</td>
          <td>加解密速度快</td>
          <td>共享同一密钥</td>
          <td>大量数据加密</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>非对称加密</td>
          <td>加解密速度慢</td>
          <td>公钥/私钥配对</td>
          <td>密钥交换、数字签名</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>哈希</td>
          <td>单向不可逆</td>
          <td>无密钥</td>
          <td>数据完整性校验、密码存储</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="对称加密">对称加密</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">明文 + 密钥 → [加密算法] → 密文
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">密文 + 密钥 → [解密算法] → 明文
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">常见算法：AES、DES、3DES、SM4</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>算法</th>
          <th>密钥长度</th>
          <th>安全性</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>AES</td>
          <td>128/192/256位</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>目前主流标准</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>DES</td>
          <td>56位</td>
          <td>低</td>
          <td>已被暴力破解</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>3DES</td>
          <td>168位</td>
          <td>中</td>
          <td>DES的加强版，已逐步淘汰</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SM4</td>
          <td>128位</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>国密标准</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="非对称加密">非对称加密</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">加密：明文 + 公钥 → 密文    解密：密文 + 私钥 → 明文
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">签名：明文 + 私钥 → 签名    验签：签名 + 公钥 → 验证
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">常见算法：RSA、ECC、SM2</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>算法</th>
          <th>密钥长度</th>
          <th>特点</th>
          <th>适用场景</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>RSA</td>
          <td>2048/4096位</td>
          <td>成熟广泛</td>
          <td>数字签名、HTTPS握手</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>ECC</td>
          <td>256位</td>
          <td>同等安全下密钥更短</td>
          <td>移动端、IoT资源受限场景</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SM2</td>
          <td>256位</td>
          <td>国密标准</td>
          <td>国内合规要求</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="哈希函数">哈希函数</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">任意长度输入 → [哈希算法] → 固定长度输出（不可逆）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">特性：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 相同输入 → 相同输出
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 不同输入 → 输出几乎一定不同（碰撞概率极低）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 无法从输出反推输入</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>算法</th>
          <th>输出长度</th>
          <th>安全性</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>SHA-256</td>
          <td>256位</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>目前主流</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SHA-3</td>
          <td>可变</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>新一代标准</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>MD5</td>
          <td>128位</td>
          <td>低</td>
          <td>已发现碰撞，不推荐</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SM3</td>
          <td>256位</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>国密标准</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1明文传输密钥">问题1：明文传输密钥</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：对称加密的密钥在传输过程中被截获
<strong>解决</strong>：使用非对称加密交换对称密钥（如TLS握手），或采用安全的密钥分发机制</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>